overview: Young, beautiful and horny, that s how we like our girls here at Private and Kris the Fox is back again to prove it! This beauty returns to us as sexy as ever and is joined by the gorgeous Roxy Sky for a threesome with a lucky guy they just met at the park. There s also Polina Sweet, another one of our usual suspects looking to let loose all her sexual frustration after months in quarantine. And finally we introduce you to Nika and Keoki Star, two teens who have come for their Private debuts looking to build a legacy, with Keoki starting off strong and impressing in a quality squirting scene. These are the stories of Private Specials, Young Nymphos 3, don t miss it!
title: Young Nymphos 3
